OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Ed Davey 'sorry'
OL,4,Cfor taking five months to meet Alan
OL,5,CBates
OL,7,FBates wrote to Davey in 2010 outlining
OL,8,Fissues with the Horizon software and
OL,9,Frequesting a meeting with the newly
OL,10,Fappointed minister.
OL,12,FDavey wrote back at the time: "I do
OL,13,Fnot believe a meeting would serve any
OL,14,Fuseful purpose".
