OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Ed Davey 'sorry'
OL,4,Cfor taking five months to meet Alan
OL,5,CBates
OL,7,FMore than 700 sub-postmasters were
OL,8,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,9,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,10,F1999 and 2015, as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,11,FHorizon system made it appear as
OL,12,Fthough money was missing at their
OL,13,Fbranches.
OL,15,FWhen Davey was interviewed by ITV
OL,16,FNews' UK Editor Paul Brand in January
OL,17,F2024, he refused to apologise for his
OL,18,Frole in the scandal, despite being
OL,19,Fasked more than 10 times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
