OL,4,Cfor taking five months to meet Alan
OL,5,CBates
OL,7,FEarlier today, a Labour Minister told
OL,8,Fthe Post Office inquiry that he
OL,9,F"relied on people telling us the
OL,10,Ftruth".
OL,12,FAnother former postal affairs
OL,13,Fminister, Pat McFadden, says
OL,14,Fpoliticians were "very reliant" on
OL,15,Finformation shared with them as they
OL,16,Fmade decisions about Horizon's IT
OL,17,Ffailures.
