OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Ed Davey 'sorry'
OL,4,Cfor taking five months to meet Alan
OL,5,CBates
OL,7,FThe Cabinet Minister later told the
OL,8,FPost Office inquiry that wrong
OL,9,Finformation led to "terrible human
OL,10,Fconsequences for some of the people
OL,11,Fhere."
OL,13,FThe inquiry was shown letters from
OL,14,FMPs, raising concerns about the
OL,15,Faccuracy of the Horizon accounting
OL,16,Fsoftware.
OL,18,FThey raised the case of Julian Wilson,
OL,19,Fwho was suspended on the assumption he
OL,20,Fwas "making false cash declarations"
OL,21,Fback in 2008.
