OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Ed Davey 'sorry'
OL,4,Cfor taking five months to meet Alan
OL,5,CBates
OL,7,FTheir post office was down #27,000
OL,8,Fover a five year period. They said
OL,9,Fthat three other postmasters raised
OL,10,Fsimilar concerns, but the Post Office
OL,11,Fwas left to reply to the concern and
OL,12,Fdeal with the case.
OL,14,FJacqui Smith, their local MP, even
OL,15,Fwrote highlighting how "there could be
OL,16,Fa system problem here", but Mr
OL,17,FMcFadden did not recall the letter.
