OL,7,FMr McFadden also recommended that the
OL,8,FChair of the Post Office Horizon IT
OL,9,FInquiry, Sir Wyn Williams, consider
OL,10,Fbringing in an independent
OL,11,Finspectorate.
OL,13,FThis body could come in "when the
OL,14,Flevel of allegations reaches such a
OL,15,Fpoint where it looks like that is the
OL,16,Fright thing to do."
